snippet.title: Festival Tycoon Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Festival Tycoon is now available in Early Access on Steam! Get it here: https://s.team/a/1326270


Create and manage your own music festival empire. Book bands, setup stages, organise your line-up, layout tents and toilets, roll out the food trucks and build your festival’s reputation to appease sponsors and earn big bucks 💰

Discord: https://discord.gg/festivaltycoon
Twitter: https://twitter.com/festivaltycoon
Website: https://festivaltycoon.dreihausstudio.com
